data.description: Why wait to build? Step into this 2020 POOL HOME, custom Split Plan  4/3/2 on 1.06 acres. You will find 10’ ceilings throughout the home, with tray ceilings in the Master & Great Room. The partial stone elevation, 8' doors and side-load garage add that extra touch to its curb appeal! You will find a separate office/den for your “work at home” needs. The Great room, master suite & hall French doors all lead to the POOL & LANAI. The Master Bath boasts Dual Sinks, Ceramic tile shower & corner whirlpool tub! Or, choose to relish in your Heated spa & Heated inground saltwater pool. The covered patio runs the length of the home with 2 ceiling fans, custom pavers for the covered patio, 31’ X 38’ lanai, and deck around the pool/spa. The second and third bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom- perfect for guests. The third bathroom is right next to the fourth bedroom (has been set up as a theatre room at present) with easy access to the lanai & pool through the french door next to bathroom. So many high-end features in this custom built "GRACIE" include crown molding, 5 1/4" base boards, GRANITE countertops, high ceilings…...  Irrigation installed, dual pane windows, prewired internet in all rooms! Closed circuit camera system with pool alarm. This is a smart home! Control it from anywhere with your phone. Enjoy your evenings on the covered front porch or relax by the pool and spa in the privacy of your homesite lined with trees on 3 sides. Owners have installed a 50 AMP hook up for guests arriving in their RV!  And Best of ALL, it’s move in ready! The new entrance to Suncoast Hwy to Tampa is minutes away!  See Spec sheet with photos! Call for your tour today!
